hopobject.body: I love this site cheap differin There were two turning points. The first came after the Giants moved into position to regain the lead just before halftime when Manning, on first down from the Broncos 28, was flushed out of the pocket and intercepted in the end zone, where Hakeem Nicks was double covered. Manning expected Nicks to go outside and he didn't - but he also missed seeing Victor Cruz open underneath, the second time in the game where pass pressure forced him to miss seeing an open man.
